WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:31.097
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 7=

01:31.912 --> 01:33.852
(Is this a date?)

01:35.127 --> 01:37.303
I also rented an apartment with Juemei.

01:37.327 --> 01:38.868
I live there on weekends.

01:39.008 --> 01:41.144
This community is where my parents live.

01:41.168 --> 01:42.583
As it's close to the exhibition hall,

01:42.607 --> 01:43.948
parking is convenient.

01:46.247 --> 01:51.308
- You've lived here since childhood?
- Yes.

01:53.127 --> 01:54.508
It's very quiet.

01:55.247 --> 01:57.023
Do you want to note down my number?

01:57.047 --> 01:58.903
In case it's crowded
and we are scattered.

01:58.927 --> 02:00.348
It will be easier to find you.

02:02.487 --> 02:04.427
- Okay.
- Give me your phone.

02:16.047 --> 02:17.047
It rings.

02:19.530 --> 02:21.782
(New contact: Mo Qingcheng)

02:23.784 --> 02:26.343
(New contact: Sheng)

02:26.367 --> 02:29.628
- Okay.
- Let's go.

02:50.087 --> 02:51.908
Happy Valentine's Day to you two.

02:52.927 --> 02:54.147
Thank you.

02:55.288 --> 02:58.147
There are quite a lot of people today.

03:07.248 --> 03:10.068
Over there are a pair of
cosers in couple skins.

03:10.968 --> 03:12.188
You play it too?

03:12.968 --> 03:16.027
Well, not actually,
but I've written fan songs for them.

03:16.288 --> 03:17.748
What a coincidence.

03:18.927 --> 03:20.107
Coincidence?

03:21.248 --> 03:23.707
- Let's check over there.
- Okay.

03:30.207 --> 03:31.987
Qiang Qingci?

03:36.408 --> 03:38.343
How come you have
free time to visit today?

03:38.367 --> 03:41.427
I happened to have time today,
so I came to look around.

03:41.848 --> 03:43.628
I am sorry.

03:43.688 --> 03:45.068
It's fine.

03:47.168 --> 03:48.188
Are you okay?

03:54.728 --> 03:55.463
This is...

03:55.487 --> 03:56.903
Shengshengman.

03:56.927 --> 03:58.183
I know.

03:58.207 --> 03:59.384
You've been low-key for years.

03:59.408 --> 04:01.908
But this time, it's all over the world.

04:03.327 --> 04:04.424
This is Mo Bai.

04:04.448 --> 04:05.568
- Hello.
- Hello.

04:05.568 --> 04:08.527
Have you listened to the fan song sung
by Qiang Qingci for Honor Of Kings?

04:08.527 --> 04:10.703
Yes. I even set it as my ringtone.

04:10.727 --> 04:11.344
Send it to me.

04:11.368 --> 04:12.048
I haven't yet.

04:12.048 --> 04:13.907
(No wonder he said it's a coincidence.)

04:16.167 --> 04:19.024
You have to be careful of
being surrounded by his fans.

04:19.048 --> 04:20.467
Shengshengman.

04:23.767 --> 04:25.584
Mr. Mo Bai, it's time to go on stage.

04:25.608 --> 04:26.584
Mu is waiting for you.

04:26.608 --> 04:28.823
Okay. I'm going to the stage. See you.

04:28.847 --> 04:29.864
- Okay. Go ahead.
- Bye.

04:29.888 --> 04:31.068
- Bye.
- Bye.

04:33.808 --> 04:35.628
He has a partner named Mu.

04:36.928 --> 04:38.587
They will be performing soon.

04:51.527 --> 04:53.428
That white-haired one is Mu.

04:57.767 --> 04:59.907
One is Zhuge Liang.
The other is Zhao Yun.

05:11.488 --> 05:13.027
Do you want to buy souvenirs?

05:13.527 --> 05:15.068
- Alright.
- Let's go.

05:16.847 --> 05:18.344
The flowers you bought are pretty.

05:18.368 --> 05:20.344
- Do you like them?
- I do.

05:20.368 --> 05:21.167
Thank you, my dear.

05:21.167 --> 05:22.904
- I love you so much.
- Me too.

05:22.928 --> 05:24.104
What are we going to eat?

05:24.128 --> 05:25.888
- Let's go for hotpot.
- Sounds good.

05:25.888 --> 05:27.548
Happy holiday, darling.

05:27.847 --> 05:28.527
Is this for me?

05:28.527 --> 05:29.584
Are your hands cold?

05:29.608 --> 05:31.707
- Kind of.
- Let me warm them for you.

05:31.847 --> 05:33.167
Do you like it? I picked it specially.

05:33.167 --> 05:34.167
Happy Valentine's Day.

05:34.167 --> 05:35.087
I like it. Thanks.

05:35.087 --> 05:36.623
(Point)
Not cold now. Thank you.

05:36.647 --> 05:39.647
(Today is really
an auspicious even-numbered day).

05:39.647 --> 05:41.688
(Hold your hand, and grow old with you)

05:41.688 --> 05:42.707
Thank you.

05:48.888 --> 05:49.888
Yummy?

06:07.688 --> 06:08.948
Juemei.

06:13.167 --> 06:14.508
Hello.

06:14.608 --> 06:17.147
- You are...?
- Yes.

06:17.767 --> 06:19.267
I'm Juemei.

06:21.008 --> 06:23.344
You came here for a date, right?

06:23.368 --> 06:24.344
No.

06:24.368 --> 06:27.143
I didn't know it was Valentine's Day.

06:27.167 --> 06:30.104
Don't worry. I will definitely not
leak anything online.

06:30.128 --> 06:31.267
Absolutely not.

06:31.368 --> 06:34.104
I've been listening to your audio drama
for ten years already.

06:34.128 --> 06:35.227
Sign, please.

06:37.647 --> 06:42.248
You're not Geng...?

06:42.248 --> 06:43.868
Sign and I'll leave.

06:43.967 --> 06:46.548
Before your girlfriend arrives.
In case of any misunderstandings.

06:57.608 --> 06:58.628
Take a photo.

07:01.087 --> 07:02.147
The V sign.

07:02.488 --> 07:04.388
Three, two, one, yeah.

07:08.287 --> 07:09.984
May your dubbing team
get better and better.

07:10.008 --> 07:11.188
Thank you.

07:28.888 --> 07:29.948
(I'm here.)

07:36.368 --> 07:37.508
Here, here, here.

07:43.448 --> 07:44.868
Geng Xiaoxing.

07:48.407 --> 07:50.347
Hello, I'm Juemei.

07:51.248 --> 07:52.428
You're welcome.

07:55.527 --> 07:57.587
So cute.

07:59.287 --> 08:00.548
Which one do you like?

08:00.888 --> 08:02.948
No, thanks. I'll pay myself.

08:03.407 --> 08:06.188
Really. I can do it myself.

08:07.207 --> 08:08.703
Hello, do you have a complete set?

08:08.727 --> 08:11.147
Do you mean a couple set?

08:12.087 --> 08:12.904
No need for that.

08:12.928 --> 08:14.608
Which character does
your girlfriend like?

08:14.608 --> 08:16.628
I can find a couple set for you.

08:19.327 --> 08:20.667
Which character?

08:22.167 --> 08:24.348
Or, you want them all.

08:25.447 --> 08:28.743
No need. This one and this one.

08:28.767 --> 08:30.608
These two are popular among girls.

08:30.608 --> 08:31.944
Then I'll wrap them up for you.

08:31.968 --> 08:35.464
- You want Mu and Mo Bai's autographs?
- Okay.

08:35.488 --> 08:36.944
Hello, don't wrap them up yet.

08:36.968 --> 08:37.903
We'll go for the signs.

08:37.927 --> 08:39.708
All right. Here you are.

08:40.167 --> 08:41.468
I've paid.

08:42.008 --> 08:43.787
Are you two cosers?

08:44.368 --> 08:44.984
No.

08:45.008 --> 08:46.783
I just saw you talking to Mo Bai.

08:46.807 --> 08:48.663
I thought you were from the same circle,

08:48.687 --> 08:49.984
just without coser make-ups.

08:50.008 --> 08:51.947
But you two are really good-looking.

08:52.527 --> 08:53.503
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

08:53.527 --> 08:54.947
Then let's go line up.

08:57.447 --> 09:00.228
Mu and Mo Bai, can you
sign autographs for me?

09:03.687 --> 09:04.224
Thank you.

09:04.248 --> 09:05.628
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

09:06.328 --> 09:07.344
Am I seeing things?

09:07.368 --> 09:08.088
No, you're not.

09:08.088 --> 09:10.267
This is the famous Shengshengman.

09:11.287 --> 09:13.944
Hello, may I take a photo with you?

09:13.968 --> 09:16.187
- No problem at all.
- Come on.

09:16.687 --> 09:17.828
Thank you.

09:19.647 --> 09:25.868
One, two, three, and done.

09:26.088 --> 09:27.147
Thank you.

09:27.248 --> 09:29.623
Can you sign an autograph for me?

09:29.647 --> 09:32.988
- Sure. Come on.
- Here.

09:33.431 --> 09:35.452
(Mo Bai)

09:36.647 --> 09:39.388
This is a special heart for my brother.

09:40.687 --> 09:41.903
What would you like me to sign?

09:41.927 --> 09:43.104
Best wishes for happiness?

09:43.128 --> 09:46.064
No. It should be "May you hear
the patter of tiny feet soon."

09:46.088 --> 09:48.787
Alright. Joking should have a limit.

09:49.208 --> 09:51.543
You brought her over
and won't let us joke?

09:51.567 --> 09:52.423
Exactly.

09:52.447 --> 09:53.547
Alright, alright.

09:55.523 --> 09:57.820
(Mu)

09:59.167 --> 10:01.348
Nice to meet you.

10:01.447 --> 10:02.984
Thank you. Nice to meet you.

10:03.008 --> 10:05.864
You go on with your business.
We won't disturb you.

10:05.888 --> 10:07.104
Let's eat together later.

10:07.128 --> 10:08.547
No, thanks. We're leaving.

10:08.647 --> 10:09.263
Fine.

10:09.287 --> 10:10.224
- Bye.
- Bye.

10:10.248 --> 10:11.267
Goodbye.

10:13.287 --> 10:15.263
So it's the two of us to eat again.

10:15.287 --> 10:16.464
I don't have time for you.

10:16.488 --> 10:18.783
When this ends,
I need to pick up my sister for my mom.

10:18.807 --> 10:20.549
Isn't it Sunday today?

10:21.128 --> 10:22.947
She is going to the amusement park.

10:23.567 --> 10:27.388
Oh my. It's so boring eating alone.

10:27.927 --> 10:30.184
You have to butt in
when I'm dining with my sister?

10:30.208 --> 10:32.748
Sounds good. Can you take me? Please.

10:33.008 --> 10:34.064
All right.

10:34.088 --> 10:35.464
Anyway, my sister likes you.

10:35.488 --> 10:37.023
If we go together, she will be happy.

10:37.047 --> 10:38.468
Exactly.

10:38.567 --> 10:39.623
- Hello.
- Can we take a photo?

10:39.647 --> 10:40.344
Sure, sure.

10:40.368 --> 10:41.128
I'll help you take it.

10:41.128 --> 10:42.468
Stand in the middle.

10:51.647 --> 10:55.104
(How should I explain
I didn't know today is Valentine's Day?)

10:55.128 --> 10:57.748
(Is it too much
to take out the contract now?)

10:58.088 --> 11:00.468
(Forget it. I'll pretend I don't know.)

11:00.888 --> 11:02.508
(Forget it. Maybe later.)

11:03.407 --> 11:05.464
Hello, would you like to order
a Valentine's Day set meal?

11:05.488 --> 11:07.508
(Love at first sight)
It is popular today.

11:11.088 --> 11:13.304
(Love at first sight)
Then we'll have this one. Thanks.

11:13.328 --> 11:14.787
Okay. Wait a moment.

11:20.407 --> 11:22.927
The reason for meeting you today
is to sign this contract.

11:22.927 --> 11:24.383
(Cooperation Agreement)
Look.

11:24.407 --> 11:25.547
Okay.

11:27.167 --> 11:28.824
This is just a part of the procedure.

11:28.848 --> 11:31.344
It will facilitate our administration
to do the follow-up work.

11:31.368 --> 11:34.228
But rest assured.
This contract does not involve money.

11:41.608 --> 11:45.388
Since you've said that,
let me be honest.

11:48.687 --> 11:51.147
I didn't know today is Valentine's Day.

11:51.807 --> 11:53.228
Don't overthink it.

11:54.008 --> 11:55.588
I didn't overthink.

11:55.848 --> 11:58.267
I didn't know today
is Valentine's Day either.

11:59.848 --> 12:01.027
I see.

12:18.167 --> 12:19.787
(Is this a date?)

12:32.567 --> 12:33.787
Hold on for a moment.

12:38.208 --> 12:39.468
Hello, Director Liu.

12:41.567 --> 12:43.228
Okay. I got it.

12:43.407 --> 12:45.628
I'll be back right away. Okay.

12:51.208 --> 12:54.508
I'm sorry. I might have to leave
as something happened at the hospital.

12:54.888 --> 12:57.224
No worries. We've pretty much
finished our tour here.

12:57.248 --> 13:00.067
- You better take off now.
- I'm sorry.

13:00.407 --> 13:02.464
No need to apologize. I understand.

13:02.488 --> 13:05.348
I told you we have
several doctors in my family.

13:05.488 --> 13:06.547
Better leave.

13:13.407 --> 13:16.143
(Should I say
I need to go back to school first?)

13:16.167 --> 13:18.067
(So as not to delay his work.)

13:20.287 --> 13:21.468
Cheng.

13:22.687 --> 13:23.748
Uncle.

13:24.687 --> 13:27.184
Haven't seen you for a while,
you naughty boy.

13:27.208 --> 13:28.508
You look more handsome.

13:28.647 --> 13:31.348
She is...?

13:31.767 --> 13:32.828
Gu Sheng.

13:33.047 --> 13:34.388
This is my uncle.

13:35.287 --> 13:36.667
Uncle, nice to meet you.

13:37.128 --> 13:38.344
Gu Sheng.

13:38.368 --> 13:39.828
This is your girlfriend?

13:40.368 --> 13:41.464
You know what?

13:41.488 --> 13:44.427
Our Mo family's daughters-in-laws
are all exceptional.

13:46.088 --> 13:47.064
Your parents.

13:47.088 --> 13:48.807
I haven't seen them
for more than a week.

13:48.807 --> 13:50.064
Go back and tell them

13:50.088 --> 13:52.228
we must get together over the weekend.

13:52.287 --> 13:53.984
They went out for a seminar.

13:54.008 --> 13:55.143
I'll do it when they get back.

13:55.167 --> 13:57.903
It's harder to schedule with family
than it is with outsiders.

13:57.927 --> 13:58.704
Well then.

13:58.728 --> 13:59.503
Later,

13:59.527 --> 14:02.023
let Cheng take you to my house.

14:02.047 --> 14:03.584
Your aunt cooks really well.

14:03.608 --> 14:05.628
We'll prepare a big meal for you then.

14:05.687 --> 14:06.824
Understood, Uncle.

14:06.848 --> 14:08.427
That's settled then.

14:08.687 --> 14:09.824
I have to go.

14:09.848 --> 14:10.488
Take care, Uncle.

14:10.488 --> 14:12.187
- Bye.
- Bye, Uncle.

14:22.008 --> 14:23.464
I'll return to the hospital.

14:23.488 --> 14:25.468
I'll drop you off at the supermarket.

14:27.927 --> 14:28.988
Alright.

14:31.208 --> 14:33.427
Let's go. I'm a bit in a hurry.

14:33.767 --> 14:35.828
Okay, then let's go.

14:40.248 --> 14:42.388
Give me your bag.

14:46.108 --> 14:47.208
Thank you.

14:48.008 --> 14:48.704
Is it hot?

14:48.728 --> 14:52.307
- Want to take off the down jacket?
- Alright.

15:05.728 --> 15:06.867
Let's go.

15:40.567 --> 15:41.567
We're here.

15:42.968 --> 15:44.623
I'll be going then.

15:44.647 --> 15:47.588
I'll try to finish my work quickly.
Let's have dinner together.

15:48.328 --> 15:49.388
No need.

15:53.567 --> 15:57.748
I have to go home
for dinner tonight. Rain check.

16:01.047 --> 16:02.023
Wait a second.

16:02.047 --> 16:05.588
Put on your down jacket and backpack
before getting out of the car.

16:28.128 --> 16:31.988
Alright, I'll call you tonight.

16:52.927 --> 16:54.388
- Bye.
- Bye.

16:58.888 --> 17:00.344
Did you celebrate Valentine's Day?

17:00.368 --> 17:03.028
You said you wouldn't be coming home.
Why you're back?

17:03.328 --> 17:06.108
Okay, help me watch for a while.

17:06.808 --> 17:07.328
I have to go.

17:07.328 --> 17:09.507
There's an event in the evening.

17:12.128 --> 17:13.187
Yiru.

17:41.808 --> 17:44.348
Do you all meet there?

17:44.808 --> 17:46.108
It's just me and you.

17:50.927 --> 17:52.744
Do you want to note down my number?

17:52.768 --> 17:54.824
In case it gets crowded
and we get separated.

17:54.848 --> 17:56.308
It'll be easier to find you.

17:57.007 --> 17:58.907
Happy Valentine's Day to both of you.

17:59.167 --> 18:00.388
Thank you.

18:03.768 --> 18:05.048
I'm sorry.

18:05.048 --> 18:05.784
It's okay.

18:05.808 --> 18:06.947
Are you okay?

18:08.927 --> 18:10.504
Which character does
your girlfriend like?

18:10.528 --> 18:12.707
I can find a couple set for you.

18:13.447 --> 18:14.223
Gu Sheng.

18:14.247 --> 18:15.588
This is your girlfriend?

18:15.848 --> 18:16.943
You know what?

18:16.967 --> 18:19.747
Our Mo family's daughters-in-laws
are all exceptional.

18:24.768 --> 18:25.903
(What would you like me to sign?)

18:25.927 --> 18:27.143
(Best wishes for happiness?)

18:27.167 --> 18:28.223
(No.)

18:28.247 --> 18:30.707
(It should be "May you hear
the patter of tiny feet soon.")

18:45.848 --> 18:47.707
(What on earth are his thoughts?)

18:48.247 --> 18:50.467
(Be calm, Shengshengman.)

18:50.927 --> 18:52.548
(Calm down.)

18:53.368 --> 18:54.628
Shengshengman?

18:56.128 --> 18:58.143
Shengshengman!

18:58.167 --> 19:00.983
Oh, my. It's really you.

19:01.007 --> 19:01.623
Oh, my.

19:01.647 --> 19:03.663
How did I not realize it was you?

19:03.687 --> 19:05.584
Ever since I found out
you are my idol's girlfriend,

19:05.608 --> 19:07.504
I seriously listened to
all your recordings

19:07.528 --> 19:09.344
from your birthday parties and concerts.

19:09.368 --> 19:11.064
How did I not realize it was you?

19:11.088 --> 19:14.024
So amazing! Oh, my!

19:14.048 --> 19:15.223
I-I am not.

19:15.247 --> 19:16.907
Impossible. You certainly are.

19:17.088 --> 19:19.088
I r-really am not.

19:19.088 --> 19:20.768
Stop pretending. I won't believe it.

19:20.768 --> 19:22.828
You certainly are.

19:23.848 --> 19:25.264
Well, don't worry.

19:25.288 --> 19:26.544
I'm the only one who knows this.

19:26.568 --> 19:27.824
I won't tell anyone.

19:27.848 --> 19:29.608
I will carry the secret to the grave.

19:29.608 --> 19:30.747
Don't worry.

19:33.007 --> 19:34.824
How did you know I...?

19:34.848 --> 19:36.848
In fact, it was Mo Bai
who just made a Weibo post.

19:36.848 --> 19:39.028
I'll show you. Check it out.

19:39.247 --> 19:40.483
This is the Weibo post he made.

19:40.507 --> 19:42.428
(Coser Mo Bai: My bad. I deleted it.)
It has been widely reposted.

19:42.447 --> 19:45.504
Then Mo Bai deleted it right away.

19:45.528 --> 19:47.568
Can you believe I even caught it?

19:47.568 --> 19:50.024
Oh, my. I am so lucky, right?

19:50.048 --> 19:51.427
Oh, my.

19:53.288 --> 19:55.784
Sheng, don't worry.

19:55.808 --> 19:58.788
I promise I won't tell anyone.

19:59.368 --> 20:00.264
But you have no idea

20:00.288 --> 20:02.383
how thrilled I was
when I recognized you.

20:02.407 --> 20:03.808
There's a "Sheng" in your name.

20:03.808 --> 20:06.423
But why didn't I think of it?

20:06.447 --> 20:08.868
W-What did he post?

20:09.207 --> 20:11.987
He just posted
a silhouette photo of you two.

20:12.407 --> 20:15.143
I mainly noticed the bag and sack
you just brought back.

20:15.167 --> 20:16.983
And your outfit and hairstyle.

20:17.007 --> 20:19.227
I knew right away that it must be you.

20:19.288 --> 20:21.344
At first, Mo Bai
didn't say anything about the photo.

20:21.368 --> 20:24.467
But once Mu reposted it,
everyone understood it.

20:24.768 --> 20:27.068
Let me show you. Look.

20:27.207 --> 20:29.024
Look at what he said
when he reposted it.

20:29.048 --> 20:31.344
(Coser Mu)
Aren't they Qiang Qingci and his wife?

20:31.368 --> 20:32.504
Do you know?

20:32.528 --> 20:35.623
Mu is my favorite coser.

20:35.647 --> 20:37.703
If I hadn't been keeping
an eye on him at all times,

20:37.727 --> 20:39.864
I would have missed this.

20:39.888 --> 20:40.568
But don't worry.

20:40.568 --> 20:41.663
He deleted it in a second.

20:41.687 --> 20:42.784
Right away.

20:42.808 --> 20:44.864
I guess many people
didn't have time to capture it.

20:44.888 --> 20:47.108
Just me. I...

20:47.247 --> 20:48.183
Oh, my.

20:48.207 --> 20:49.128
Stay calm.

20:49.128 --> 20:50.223
Sheng,

20:50.247 --> 20:52.888
you have no idea how many years
I've been a fan of Qiang Qingci.

20:52.888 --> 20:57.423
Do you know how I've been coping with it
over the years?

20:57.447 --> 20:59.427
Excuse me, do you have basins?

21:00.368 --> 21:01.868
Welcome.

21:15.328 --> 21:16.183
Sheng!

21:16.207 --> 21:18.264
Hold on. Wait a minute.

21:18.288 --> 21:19.907
I have one last question.

21:20.007 --> 21:22.987
The doctor who came to
our store the other day.

21:25.647 --> 21:27.584
He wants to pursue you?
He is trying to steal you away?

21:27.608 --> 21:29.388
Even away from my idol?

21:30.247 --> 21:31.463
I get it right, don't I?

21:31.487 --> 21:33.227
No.

21:34.288 --> 21:39.427
He is just my senior
from next-door college.

21:39.568 --> 21:43.147
He's quite nice. Just a bit quiet.

21:43.568 --> 21:45.947
Okay, then. I can rest assured.

21:46.288 --> 21:47.264
I'll be leaving.

21:47.288 --> 21:48.903
Alright. Bye. Oh!

21:48.927 --> 21:50.947
Could you say hello to my idol for me?

21:51.288 --> 21:52.907
Alright. Bye.

21:57.967 --> 22:00.423
The senior from next-door college.

22:00.447 --> 22:01.828
What is that?

22:31.048 --> 22:32.048
Arrived.

22:34.768 --> 22:36.183
Thank you.

22:36.207 --> 22:38.383
Sorry to interrupt your Valentine's Day.

22:38.407 --> 22:40.747
No problem. I'm free today anyway.

22:47.487 --> 22:48.628
Bye.

22:50.128 --> 22:51.268
Bye.

23:21.608 --> 23:23.108
Mom, I'm back.

23:23.967 --> 23:26.223
Why didn't you tell me
in advance when you headed back?

23:26.247 --> 23:27.784
I didn't leave any food for you.

23:27.808 --> 23:31.467
No. I was at a friend's house nearby,
so I came back.

23:33.007 --> 23:34.868
Mom, why are you packing?

23:35.687 --> 23:37.983
Your father and I are going to
take care of your grandfather today.

23:38.007 --> 23:39.388
Grandfather?

23:39.447 --> 23:40.703
Isn't he at home?

23:40.727 --> 23:42.548
Your grandfather is in the hospital.

23:42.848 --> 23:44.388
In the hospital?

23:44.967 --> 23:48.143
Is he okay? Which hospital is he in?
What happened to him?

23:48.167 --> 23:50.623
It's the hospital
across from our supermarket.

23:50.647 --> 23:52.068
I don't know either.

23:52.808 --> 23:55.344
He went for a check-up by himself.

23:55.368 --> 23:58.028
When he was at the hospital,
the doctor said

23:58.128 --> 24:00.463
it would be best to have
a comprehensive check-up.

24:00.487 --> 24:02.467
Then he called me.

24:02.967 --> 24:04.423
Your grandfather is aged now.

24:04.447 --> 24:07.028
It's a good thing
to have a check-up in the hospital.

24:07.647 --> 24:09.663
I'll go with you.

24:09.687 --> 24:14.460
(Hospitalization Department)

24:15.808 --> 24:19.223
Grandpa, next time,
let any of us accompany you.

24:19.247 --> 24:21.108
Please don't come by yourself.

24:21.568 --> 24:22.744
It's okay.

24:22.768 --> 24:24.943
It's just my students

24:24.967 --> 24:27.104
who heard I hadn't
had a check-up in a long time.

24:27.128 --> 24:28.824
They insisted
that I stay here for a few days.

24:28.848 --> 24:31.467
Once all the check-ups are done,
I'll be discharged.

24:33.328 --> 24:34.504
As long as you're fine.

24:34.528 --> 24:36.864
Grandpa, I'll see
if there's anything delicious outside.

24:36.888 --> 24:39.108
- I'll get something for you.
- That's great.

24:39.207 --> 24:40.264
I'm leaving.

24:40.288 --> 24:41.463
Don't buy just anything.

24:41.487 --> 24:42.223
I know.

24:42.247 --> 24:44.268
Here, Dad, have an orange.

24:44.407 --> 24:46.227
You go back too.

24:47.888 --> 24:49.907
(Which department is he in?)

24:50.608 --> 24:52.068
(Which floor is it on?)

25:04.167 --> 25:05.187
Sheng.

25:15.447 --> 25:16.504
What a coincidence.

25:16.528 --> 25:17.684
What are you doing here?

25:17.708 --> 25:19.227
This is for hospitalization.

25:20.848 --> 25:22.503
My grandpa is here.

25:22.527 --> 25:24.108
Your grandpa got hospitalized?

25:24.447 --> 25:27.544
He's fine. He's just here for a check-up
and will be discharged in a few days.

25:27.568 --> 25:29.183
My grandpa used to be a doctor,

25:29.207 --> 25:31.304
so he prefers to come here
by himself when he's ill.

25:31.328 --> 25:33.423
No matter his age,
he always comes alone.

25:33.447 --> 25:34.588
Which bed is he in?

25:34.967 --> 25:36.308
Bed nineteen.

25:39.727 --> 25:43.068
Are you checking your patients?

25:43.167 --> 25:44.828
I came over for someone.

25:44.888 --> 25:46.383
My department's wards aren't here.

25:46.407 --> 25:47.788
I'm in cardiac surgery.

25:51.720 --> 25:53.244
When will you go home?

25:54.088 --> 25:55.868
I guess I'll be heading back soon.

26:00.207 --> 26:04.548
- It's fine. Go ahead. Don't mind me.
- Okay.

26:06.048 --> 26:07.628
- Bye.
- Bye.

26:16.723 --> 26:17.727
(Hospitalization Department)

26:17.727 --> 26:19.947
Grandpa, you go ahead.
I'm heading back now.

26:23.576 --> 26:25.788
(Cardiac Surgery Department)

26:28.808 --> 26:31.947
(Should I go and say goodbye to him?)

26:55.808 --> 26:58.328
Dad, time for dinner.
Tomatoes and scrambled eggs.

26:58.328 --> 27:00.463
The doctor said it.
Drink some water first.

27:00.487 --> 27:01.104
Water.

27:01.128 --> 27:03.348
No, thanks. I can manage.

27:14.207 --> 27:15.308
You're back?

27:15.487 --> 27:19.348
Calling you back
must have interrupted your date, huh?

27:21.447 --> 27:22.467
It's alright.

27:26.808 --> 27:28.187
You really had a date?

27:30.687 --> 27:34.667
Is it the Miss Clam
from the call last time?

27:34.888 --> 27:35.983
Listen,

27:36.007 --> 27:37.903
even if the girl has a nice temper,

27:37.927 --> 27:39.828
you still need to apologize to her.

27:41.568 --> 27:42.667
Really.

28:11.888 --> 28:13.628
Are you busy?

28:18.391 --> 28:21.005
(Voice message)

28:21.608 --> 28:23.983
Hold on. I just finished showering.

28:24.007 --> 28:25.388
I'll just get dressed.

28:34.153 --> 28:36.188
(Mo Qingcheng)

28:40.487 --> 28:43.308
- Hello?
- Are you in a hurry to talk to me?

28:45.088 --> 28:46.388
Not really.

28:46.888 --> 28:51.427
- I forgot to ask you something.
- Go ahead.

29:00.048 --> 29:04.868
The song we recorded that day.

29:05.487 --> 29:08.507
You said it would be released
on Valentine's Day.

29:17.007 --> 29:18.147
Return With You?

29:18.808 --> 29:20.987
Yes, Return With You.

29:21.487 --> 29:22.548
What's wrong?

29:24.487 --> 29:30.707
- I'd like to know if you'll release it.
- Yes.

29:32.848 --> 29:36.507
(It seems a bit wrong
not to release a song recorded, )

29:36.888 --> 29:40.227
(but would it be
too showy to release it?)

29:40.487 --> 29:42.507
If you don't want to do so,
we can change

29:42.687 --> 29:44.584
to a different song, but they all know

29:44.608 --> 29:45.943
I planned to give a gift today.

29:45.967 --> 29:47.868
So, I have to release it.

29:50.288 --> 29:51.467
That's true.

29:52.088 --> 29:53.868
Do you have any existing arrangements?

29:53.927 --> 29:56.707
Send it to me. How about I sing it?

29:58.447 --> 29:59.507
Sure.

30:00.888 --> 30:02.667
Let me think.

30:04.328 --> 30:07.824
The latest one on my computer
is Dawn and Dusk.

30:07.848 --> 30:09.427
Let's sing this one tonight.

30:09.487 --> 30:10.423
You do the harmony.

30:10.447 --> 30:11.467
Okay.

30:14.048 --> 30:16.744
I recorded this song
by myself a few days ago.

30:16.768 --> 30:19.504
And I accompanied it
with my own guzheng playing.

30:19.528 --> 30:21.423
No major issues
with the accompaniment, I guess.

30:21.447 --> 30:23.304
Wait for a moment.
I'll process it a little more.

30:23.328 --> 30:25.548
I'll send it to you in half an hour.

30:25.848 --> 30:29.427
Okay. Bye.

30:51.078 --> 30:54.428
(Emergency, Outpatient)

31:30.967 --> 31:33.588
- Thanks.
- You're awake.

31:40.207 --> 31:41.947
You're not busy working overtime?

31:42.247 --> 31:43.183
I'm busy.

31:43.207 --> 31:45.183
But you are busier than me.

31:45.207 --> 31:47.427
So I took some time
to come take care of you.

31:49.447 --> 31:51.868
When are you going home?
Can you give me a ride?

31:52.727 --> 31:53.744
I'm waiting for something.

31:53.768 --> 31:55.507
I won't have time to drive you home.

31:58.007 --> 31:59.028
Alright.

32:00.727 --> 32:02.388
You're so heartless.

32:09.298 --> 32:11.868
(Dawn and Dusk. WAV)

32:21.048 --> 32:23.104
The contract has been signed. Look.

32:23.128 --> 32:25.068
Check out my efficiency.

32:26.328 --> 32:28.548
Quite ceremonial.

32:28.687 --> 32:31.024
Signing the contract on February 14th.

32:31.048 --> 32:32.504
What do you mean by that?

32:32.528 --> 32:34.544
I told you I was doing it by the way.

32:34.568 --> 32:37.463
Don't associate everything
with Valentine's Day.

32:37.487 --> 32:38.588
Oh.

32:39.447 --> 32:41.947
What do you mean?

32:42.288 --> 32:45.368
I told you I was passing by her school.

32:45.368 --> 32:48.947
And then, I took care of
my private and public affairs together.

32:49.647 --> 32:51.507
You don't need to report to me.

32:52.687 --> 32:54.967
Don't disturb a single young woman

32:54.967 --> 32:57.584
to work peacefully on Valentine's Day.

32:57.608 --> 32:58.628
Thank you.

32:59.727 --> 33:02.987
No. Who is reporting to you? I...

33:03.447 --> 33:04.647
You are trying to disgust me.

33:04.647 --> 33:06.024
What's gotten into you today?

33:06.048 --> 33:08.064
Did your brain get stimulated?

33:08.088 --> 33:09.788
Alright. I'm going to work now.

33:09.888 --> 33:11.628
Volunteering to work?

33:13.128 --> 33:14.088
What? Work...

33:14.088 --> 33:16.868
I'm happy. I'm cheerful.
Isn't it okay for me to work?

33:17.247 --> 33:18.507
Alright. I'm leaving.

33:22.647 --> 33:23.868
Abnormal.

33:31.528 --> 33:33.987
(Sent. You can listen to it.)

33:35.368 --> 33:38.344
(So quick. Was it done in one go?)

33:38.368 --> 33:39.628
(Truly him.)

33:40.160 --> 33:42.620
(Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci
shares the single, "Dawn and Dusk")

33:44.889 --> 33:48.229
(Dawn and Dusk by Qiang Qingci)

33:52.007 --> 33:54.947
(This song is a gift
from her and me to all of you.)

33:55.407 --> 33:56.868
(Happy Valentine's Day!)

34:12.351 --> 34:16.029
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

34:16.029 --> 34:17.064
♪ Depict a stroke ♪

34:17.064 --> 34:18.184
♪ Of rain before the mountain ♪

34:18.184 --> 34:20.380
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

34:20.799 --> 34:25.000
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

34:25.000 --> 34:27.560
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

34:27.560 --> 34:30.172
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

34:30.879 --> 34:34.568
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

34:34.568 --> 34:35.976
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

34:35.976 --> 34:39.024
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

34:39.048 --> 34:39.976
♪ On this journey ♪

34:39.976 --> 34:41.725
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

34:41.725 --> 34:44.048
♪ I walk down with you ♪

34:44.072 --> 34:48.711
♪ Spending dawns and dusks together
for a hundred years ♪

34:48.735 --> 34:51.528
(Juemei and Feng Yasong:
The promised "Return With You"?)

34:51.528 --> 34:53.628
♪ It rains ♪

34:55.814 --> 34:57.736
(The harmony is from Shengshengman?)

34:57.736 --> 35:01.448
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

35:01.448 --> 35:02.536
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

35:02.536 --> 35:05.475
(Linglong: The harmony
is from Shengshengman?)

35:06.208 --> 35:09.063
(Each time Linglong
releases a new song, )

35:09.087 --> 35:11.744
(Mr. Qiang must have a listen.)

35:11.768 --> 35:15.907
(Does our Mr. Qiang
lack songs to listen to?)

35:17.446 --> 35:19.264
(Linglong: The harmony
is from Shengshengman?)

35:19.288 --> 35:20.007
(Sheng.)

35:20.007 --> 35:21.063
(But Long, )

35:21.087 --> 35:23.328
(you haven't been on Weibo for years,
but how did you find out)

35:23.328 --> 35:25.627
(the rumored heroine for the month?)

35:26.127 --> 35:27.911
(I've known her for a long time.)

35:27.935 --> 35:30.624
♪ I hear your voice ♪

35:30.648 --> 35:33.063
(One is a top commercial voiceover.)

35:33.087 --> 35:35.987
(The other is
a great ancient-style singer.)

35:36.047 --> 35:38.148
(They must have known
each other for many years.)

35:41.967 --> 35:43.188
Have a meal.

35:47.679 --> 35:49.888
♪ Lightly falling
outside and inside the dream ♪

35:49.888 --> 35:52.864
Although it's not "Return With You,"

35:52.888 --> 35:54.903
this song also has its profundities.

35:54.927 --> 35:56.704
Right, isn't it?

35:56.728 --> 35:59.144
Even Linglong
who's been off Weibo for years

35:59.168 --> 36:00.668
has been lured out.

36:01.888 --> 36:03.427
(Linglong)
Look, this comment.

36:03.648 --> 36:06.668
"I've known her for a long time."

36:07.127 --> 36:09.784
Just think. What does that mean?

36:09.808 --> 36:11.144
What could it mean?

36:11.168 --> 36:12.903
Interesting.

36:12.927 --> 36:13.943
Think about it.

36:13.967 --> 36:18.103
It means Linglong has been observing
in secret for a long time.

36:18.127 --> 36:20.704
She can't keep a low profile
when Mr. Qiang gives a high one.

36:20.728 --> 36:24.427
Between the former rumored heroine
and the current one.

36:24.487 --> 36:25.744
Do you think Mr. Qiang

36:25.768 --> 36:27.308
feels a bit troubled this time?

36:27.927 --> 36:29.983
Troubled? Why should he?

36:30.007 --> 36:31.903
When have you ever seen
Qiang Qingci like that?

36:31.927 --> 36:33.144
Well, that's hard to say.

36:33.168 --> 36:34.808
There are many years of affection.

36:34.808 --> 36:37.423
Between long-term affection
and love at first sight.

36:37.447 --> 36:39.188
It's hard to tell who's better.

36:39.328 --> 36:40.383
Look.

36:40.407 --> 36:43.943
If Qiang Qingci really
had something for Linglong,

36:43.967 --> 36:45.103
would he have waited for years?

36:45.127 --> 36:46.704
Wouldn't he have done something by now?

36:46.728 --> 36:48.184
What do you know?

36:48.208 --> 36:49.704
How many romances have you been in?

36:49.728 --> 36:52.407
They met before they became famous.

36:52.407 --> 36:54.103
- Alright, alright.
- What's more,

36:54.127 --> 36:56.744
Linglong is also an OG
in our traditional music circle.

36:56.768 --> 36:58.907
Why are you helping outsiders?

36:59.688 --> 37:01.308
I notice you're being funny.

37:01.567 --> 37:03.103
Who's favoring outsiders?

37:03.127 --> 37:04.344
You scared me.

37:04.368 --> 37:07.023
Isn't Sheng considered part of
our traditional music circle?

37:07.047 --> 37:08.824
You're an OG yourself.

37:08.848 --> 37:10.583
- Can't you stand to see newcomers?
- I...

37:10.607 --> 37:12.023
You lack the demeanor of a senior.

37:12.047 --> 37:13.144
Wow, wow.

37:13.168 --> 37:15.228
That's not what I mean.

37:16.208 --> 37:18.188
Mao, speak up for me.

37:20.447 --> 37:22.208
Look, Mao is sober-minded.

37:22.208 --> 37:23.543
He knows that's not what I'm saying.

37:23.567 --> 37:25.027
The song is not bad.

37:27.081 --> 37:29.799
♪ Among the millions of people ♪

37:29.823 --> 37:32.318
♪ I hear your voice ♪

37:32.318 --> 37:36.732
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

37:36.808 --> 37:38.107
I didn't mean that.

37:38.487 --> 37:40.027
I'm so disappointed in you.

37:41.447 --> 37:43.168
If you leave, then leave,
but why take the food?

37:43.168 --> 37:48.610
(Emergency, Outpatient)

37:52.047 --> 37:56.144
Dr. Mo. Luckily, I catch up.

37:56.168 --> 37:58.383
You're really something.
Where are you going?

37:58.407 --> 37:59.344
Going home.

37:59.368 --> 38:00.704
You know my home the best.

38:00.728 --> 38:02.184
My mom made something yummy.

38:02.208 --> 38:04.427
Let's go back now
and you can still have it warm.

38:04.527 --> 38:05.704
Okay, I'll take you home.

38:05.728 --> 38:07.704
But I probably won't make it
in time for the meal.

38:07.728 --> 38:08.987
I have an appointment.

38:09.328 --> 38:10.864
What about tomorrow?

38:10.888 --> 38:12.668
Don't you have two days off?

38:12.728 --> 38:14.543
I'm busy tomorrow.

38:14.567 --> 38:17.148
- Let's go. Get in the car.
- Alright.

38:29.035 --> 38:32.156
(Shengshengman)
(I'm releasing an album. Could you help compose?)

38:41.652 --> 38:42.688
(Linglong)

38:42.688 --> 38:44.903
(Sorry to bother you.)

38:44.927 --> 38:46.864
(I'm releasing an album.)

38:46.888 --> 38:49.748
(Could you help compose?)

38:58.648 --> 39:00.063
(We can discuss the price later.)

39:00.087 --> 39:01.943
(Definitely no less than
the market rate.)

39:01.967 --> 39:04.668
(I want to talk to you about
the possibility of working together.)

39:11.447 --> 39:14.103
(I'm very pleased
that you think so highly of me.)

39:14.127 --> 39:17.463
(But I rarely compose to
a specific theme.)

39:17.487 --> 39:20.188
(I'm afraid I might
lack the experience.)

39:23.047 --> 39:25.224
(I've listened to all your past songs.)

39:25.248 --> 39:26.467
(I like them a lot.)

39:29.487 --> 39:31.144
(How about this?)

39:31.168 --> 39:32.744
(Tell me)

39:32.768 --> 39:35.344
(what style you usually like.)

39:35.368 --> 39:36.828
(I'll think it over.)

39:39.607 --> 39:42.587
(Have you heard of "Manman"
and "Light Ink and Sweet Lotus"?)

39:46.047 --> 39:51.907
- (Yes. Let me consider it, okay?)
- (Okay.)

39:54.888 --> 39:57.348
I'm not in a hurry.
You can drive slowly.

40:21.841 --> 40:23.516
(Mo Qingcheng)

40:31.007 --> 40:35.188
Hey, have you listened it?

40:36.288 --> 40:37.507
Yes.

40:38.047 --> 40:39.268
Have you had dinner?

40:40.768 --> 40:42.864
My parents aren't home tonight,

40:42.888 --> 40:45.107
but they left me some bread.

40:46.248 --> 40:47.587
You're eating it now?

40:55.487 --> 40:57.348
I just wrapped up.

40:57.768 --> 41:00.864
I was thinking of waiting for you
to eat something nice together

41:00.888 --> 41:03.664
to reward myself for having to
work overtime on Valentine's Day.

41:03.688 --> 41:05.748
You haven't eaten yet? It's so late.

41:07.248 --> 41:08.868
It's already eleven o'clock.

41:09.567 --> 41:10.828
I've been too busy.

41:11.728 --> 41:16.748
Rain check. I'll have dinner with you.

41:17.927 --> 41:19.228
How about tomorrow?

41:24.848 --> 41:26.148
Tomorrow?

41:27.168 --> 41:28.824
After I record
at the studio with Zhou Zheng

41:28.848 --> 41:31.304
and the others,
we're going to have dinner together.

41:31.328 --> 41:32.388
I'll pick you up.

41:35.527 --> 41:37.943
Then send me the address.

41:37.967 --> 41:39.907
I'll go there by myself tomorrow.

41:39.967 --> 41:41.027
That works too.

41:41.368 --> 41:44.023
We might come out of
the studio quite late.

41:44.047 --> 41:46.627
521 Hunan Road.

41:47.087 --> 41:49.503
Building 6, Unit 1, Apartment 1602.

41:49.527 --> 41:51.624
That's the address.
I'll send it to you then.

41:51.648 --> 41:53.228
Isn't it a restaurant?

41:55.248 --> 41:56.788
The address of my place.

41:57.447 --> 41:59.304
I'm renting it with Juemei.

41:59.328 --> 42:01.107
It's not the place you went to.

42:12.648 --> 42:13.828
Hmm.

42:16.967 --> 42:18.148
Deal?

42:19.447 --> 42:22.027
Yeah. See you tomorrow.

42:22.768 --> 42:23.788
See you.

42:35.851 --> 42:40.391
(Ancheng, Hunan Road, 521,
Jiayuan Residential Complex, )

42:40.391 --> 42:45.788
(Building 6, Unit 1, Apartment 1602.)

42:52.510 --> 42:58.460
(Building 6)

42:59.047 --> 43:00.668
Tomorrow?

43:04.888 --> 43:07.103
Shengshengman won't escape.

43:07.127 --> 43:08.624
You have to have some confidence.

43:08.648 --> 43:10.228
No need to chase her every day.

43:10.288 --> 43:12.744
Even if he wants to do so,
it's not possible.

43:12.768 --> 43:15.864
Doctors have to
squeeze out time to date.

43:15.888 --> 43:18.547
Of course, he needs to date
if he has managed to get time off.

43:18.607 --> 43:19.668
I support you.

43:20.728 --> 43:22.503
Just don't forget to
give a heads-up in advance.

43:22.527 --> 43:24.507
Your professional characteristics.

43:24.688 --> 43:26.543
Don't get so busy
that you disappear for a whole day.

43:26.567 --> 43:27.704
Right when she is kissing you,

43:27.728 --> 43:30.228
a call comes and you have to leave.
Who could stand that?

43:32.007 --> 43:33.228
Experienced, huh?

43:33.768 --> 43:36.668
My theoretical experience
is quite substantial.

43:38.407 --> 43:41.228
By the way, after work tomorrow,
you all come to my place.

43:42.127 --> 43:44.184
Wait. You two are dating

43:44.208 --> 43:45.748
and we are singing alongside.

43:48.447 --> 43:49.383
Afraid she may be shy.

43:49.407 --> 43:51.107
More at ease with more men.

43:51.768 --> 43:53.063
Okay. See you tomorrow.

43:53.087 --> 43:54.507
We will definitely go.

43:58.407 --> 44:02.308
He wouldn't always
take us around like ornaments, would he?

44:02.808 --> 44:04.983
Just cherish the present.

44:05.007 --> 44:06.784
In the future
when they're dating smoothly,

44:06.808 --> 44:08.868
they may find you annoying
if you follow them.

44:11.248 --> 44:13.607
Why should I follow him
when he is in a relationship?

44:13.607 --> 44:14.627
How strange.

44:31.607 --> 44:35.668
- I heard you went for a contract today.
- Yes.

45:10.975 --> 45:14.728
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

45:14.728 --> 45:16.008
♪ Depict a stroke ♪

45:16.008 --> 45:17.036
♪ Of rain before the mountain ♪

45:17.036 --> 45:19.335
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

45:19.359 --> 45:23.464
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

45:23.464 --> 45:26.024
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

45:26.024 --> 45:28.508
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

45:29.567 --> 45:33.288
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

45:33.288 --> 45:34.696
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

45:34.696 --> 45:37.785
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

45:37.785 --> 45:38.824
♪ On this journey ♪

45:38.824 --> 45:40.520
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

45:40.520 --> 45:42.695
♪ I walk down with you ♪

45:42.695 --> 45:47.356
♪ Spending dawns and dusks together
for a hundred years ♪

45:47.423 --> 45:49.320
♪ Just like ♪

45:49.320 --> 45:50.250
♪ When the clouds are low ♪

45:50.250 --> 45:51.875
♪ It rains ♪

45:51.875 --> 45:56.339
♪ I was moved when you were singing softly ♪

45:56.339 --> 46:00.072
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

46:00.072 --> 46:01.160
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

46:01.160 --> 46:05.633
♪ I could hear you among millions of voices ♪

46:05.633 --> 46:08.108
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

46:08.108 --> 46:10.514
♪ I hear your monologue ♪

46:10.514 --> 46:14.874
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

46:14.874 --> 46:17.320
♪ Like knowing
the implied meaning of a picture ♪

46:17.320 --> 46:19.952
♪ And the emotions in your eyes ♪

46:19.952 --> 46:23.976
♪ Feel new even after several times ♪

46:23.976 --> 46:26.632
♪ Among the millions of people ♪

46:26.632 --> 46:29.230
♪ I hear your voice ♪

46:29.230 --> 46:33.123
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

46:33.123 --> 46:35.815
♪ A sky full of stars
all over the mountains and fields ♪

46:35.815 --> 46:38.408
♪ You are my whole world ♪

46:38.408 --> 46:45.308
♪ Slowly spending
dawns and dusks with you ♪
